        "Dear Mark,",
        "Thank you for agreeing to house-sit for me. I am in relief that you will be taking care of my house.",
        "If  you need to contact me while I\u2019m away, I\u2019ll be staying at The Park Plaza Hotel, Cannought Place in New Delhi. If it\u2019s urgent, however, please call me on my mobile phone, which I\u2019ll always keep it with me. I Have written the numbers on a sticky note which I\u2019ve left on the fridge.",
        "ALSO, My Dog needs to be fed twice daily -morning and evening. So, each morning and evening put a handful of Pedigree in his dish and fresh water in his water pot. You will find the food in a jar in the kitchen cupboard. You can give him a small bowl of milk in the evening but do it every other day.",
        "I would like to request, you to water my plants, too. The indoor ones in the lounge only need water twice a week but the plants on the balcony need to be watered daily. Finally, for security, please lock the door and shut the windows before you go to bed.",
